  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.9.5">
<l>okkalai vaittu mulaippā luṇṇeṉṟu tantiṭa vāṅkic</l>
<l>cekkañ cekavaṉ ṟavaḷpā luyirceka vuṇṭa perumā</l>
<l>ṉakka pirāṉō ṭayaṉu mintira ṉummuta lāka</l>
<l>vokkavun tōṟṟiya vīcaṉ māya ṉeṉṉeñci ṉuḷāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great lord who, when she put [him] to [her] body [and] gave [him her] breast,</l>
<l>saying “drink milk”, dragged [her] destructively that day [and] drank her milk</l>
<l>so as to destroy [her] life, the smiling lord who harmoniously created,</l>
<l>along with lord [Śiva], Ayaṉ and Indra as the first, the Dark one is in my heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
